Project: Water Ripple Effect In Terminal \
In Terminal Type:\
1) ./ripple\
2) Select one position with the cursor \
3) Input a number from 1-9 and hit F3\
4) Watch the wave bounce outwards\
\
*Our project accommodates bouncing off the walls. The wave can bounce off any wall\
but bouncing off two walls is not currently possible.}